channel.title: [UPDATE] ChaoticX Release - YAY :D [614/634] [UPDATE]
channel.description:
[center] OK, this is the updated version of this server, it was released on a diff site.
Im also releasing so people can make a decent start on 614 economy, my economy did not work out, so i hope it is helpful to you all
Neways let's head to features
Godwars Nex Farming - 75% Clanwars - SafePk Working PVP drops with protect item 100% Corporeal Beast Pickup / Remove globalGroundItem Fixed (when you try to pickup or remove at a height above 0) Firemaking Woodcutting - Dementhium Team Mining Core - Softnyx Shitty PKpoint system with shops, look through source its somewhere Tormented Demons Training / Leveling Up Object spawning / removing Offer - X in trade works 100% Herblore - 100% Timer system - Softnyx Special attack fix Shitty attempt at pathfinding fix. Item on Object packet Barrows Abyssal Demons Backup system / Crash restarter - 100% credits to creator of CBU in RS2Server section Music? A start on agility Administrator commands Improved yell command
Well thats all i can remember at the moment, oh yeah, the files has a eclipse java bytecode optimizer soot, u may wanna use that too. [/center] [center]I would like to thank the dementhium team for making this happen Download: Client: http://uppit.com/b8fxgvjwiubx/Deob_output.zip (uppit looks like it is down, please be patient)[/center]
